Package: plotor
Type: Package
Title: Produces an Odds Ratio Plot from a GLM Model
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
  person(
    'Craig', 'Parylo', 
    email = 'craig.parylo2@nhs.net', 
    role = c('aut', 'cre', 'cph'),
    comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0003-4297-7808')
  )
Maintainer: Craig Parylo <craig.parylo2@nhs.net>
Description: Produces an Odds Ratio (OR) plot to visualise the result of a logistic regression analysis.
    Provide it with a model produced by glm binomial regression and it will convert the estimates to odds ratios with a 95% confidence interval and plot the results using 'ggplot2'.
